dialogue.introduction: Ye~s! It's Nenohi. Have you memorized my name? hey? Hey~!
dialogue.library_intro: I'm Nenohi, second ship of the Hatsuharu class built under the Maru-1 program. I'm working hard to organize many things for my 21st Destroyer Corps sister ships, such as Hatsuharu sister ships. What? Submarines ...? I REALLY hate them!
dialogue.secretary1: They call me Nenohi! Nenohi! Neh-Noh-Hee!
dialogue.secretary3: Admiral, don't you want to be more in sync with me?
dialogue.secretaryidle: Ahgaa~ somehow Nenohi, is bored... I'll admit that I'm bored. Let's do something Admiral, anything♪
dialogue.secretarymarried: Hey, Nenohi's worried about you too, you know? Admiral, let's take a break every now and then, okay? Nenohi will rest too～♪
dialogue.wedding: Hey, do you know day is today? ...Gee, it's Nenohi! No, that's no it, it's the day Nenohi will confess. To who, you asked? Admiral, you meanie!
dialogue.show_players_score: Admiral, Nenohi wanna look at the report too. Oh oh, Oooooh~
dialogue.joining_a_fleet: Okay, I've been waiting for it! Nenohi, setting sail!
dialogue.equipment2: I wonder what day is today?
dialogue.equipment3: Nenohi feels like she has become stronger!
dialogue.expedition_selection: Nenohi feels like she has become stronger!
dialogue.resource_collection: Nenohi feels like she has become stronger!
dialogue.instant_repair: Nenohi feels like she has become stronger!
dialogue.development: Nenohi feels like she has become stronger!
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Please let Nenohi sleep for a while.
dialogue.return_from_sortie: The fleet has returned. Thanks for your hard work~
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Okay, I've been waiting for it! Nenohi, setting sail!
dialogue.mvp: Mmhm... you give up yet? Nenohi has more than just looks, you know!
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Shooting at Nenohi, what a meanie!
dialogue.christmas_2014: Wah! It's Christmas, Christmas! Nenohi loves Christmas! ... So, what day does Christmas fall on, again...?
dialogue.new_year_2015: New year! Happy New Year! Regards for this year! Yes! Please take care of me this year too. Ok?
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: What day is it? Yep, it's Nenohi... wait, it's a special day. I did it!
dialogue.setsubun_2016: If it's February, it's got to be Nenohi.... I mean, Setsubun-- Setsubun. I'll throw the beans--, too!
